    "text": "West Chester University Digital Commons was redesigned between late 2025 and early 2026.",
    "topic": "Digital Commons Redesign"
  },
  {
    "text": "The redesign of West Chester University Digital Commons is its first since its launch in 2014.",
    "topic": "Digital Commons Redesign Timeline"
  },
  {
    "text": "The original appearance and functionality of the West Chester University Institutional Repository are being preserved during the site redesign.",
    "topic": "Repository Preservation"
  },
  {
    "text": "Archived data files are included to ensure the reproducibility of the West Chester University Digital Commons.",
    "topic": "Data Archiving"
  },
  {
    "text": "The carpet metaphor describes the West Chester University Digital Commons as a platform for an evolving archive, indicating a dynamic collection of media.",
    "topic": "Digital Commons Description"
  }
